data.description: Welcome to Battlement Mesa! This home located in the hills of Colorado has a fantastic layout and lots of fun details. The  open and bright living space effortlessly flows into the kitchen and dining area - with a gas fireplace! The bright windows and skylights ensure that you can enjoy the sunshine! The french doors to the office (or potential 3rd bedroom!) give the feeling of a bigger space while still providing privacy. The primary suite is inviting, with double doors not only at the entry but to the walk-in closet as well. And you cannot miss the beautiful clawfoot tub! The additional full bath and bedroom are both well sized and the laundry room has great rustic details. The backyard is all set for entertaining with an open patio and hot tub! Beautiful landscaping surrounds the home and there is plenty of room in the garage for toys to explore the area around Parachute. This fantastic opportunity will not last long!
